      "title": "Lock to 400 fuel stations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the new payment system introduced by the Sri Lanka Fuel Corporation, 400 fuel stations have been temporarily closed, according to the President of the Fuel Station Owners Association, Kumar Rajapaksa."
